## Import Paths

Our `tsconfig.json` is configured with module paths as follows:

```json
"paths": {
    "app/*": ["./src/app/*"],
    "~/*": ["./src/features/*"]
}
```

Use these paths when importing.

### Examples

```tsx
import { config } from "~/config"

const isDevelopment = config.overrideEnvironment === "development"
```

```tsx
import { ActionPalette } from "app/action-palette"

export default ActionPalette
```
